Esta�e Lauder Est�e Lauder Est�e Lauder Foundation Est�e Lauder Makeup Est�e Lauder Skin Care Est�e Lauder Women's Luxie Beauty Men's Fragrance Women's Fragrance Women's Perfume



Estee-LauderKnown for a vast array of skin care products, makeup and fragrances, Estee Lauder is one of the most reliable brands when it comes to consistent quality. Radiate natural beauty when you choose from a wide selection of anti-aging creams, facial cleansers, moisturizers and night creams that will ramp up your skin care regimen.Most Estee Lauder products take a multi-pronged approach to skin care by brightening dark spots and fortifying skin overall for a luminous look that lasts all day long. For an even smoother look, try a refinishing formula to help give your face a practically poreless appearance.Makeup removers that cleanse deeply while removing dirt and oil are a great first step for your nighttime skin care regimen. Follow with a gentle foaming cleanser that reinvigorates and softens your face. You can also choose refreshing toner to round out your routine. Repairing night creams are an equally perfect choice for restoring and maintaining your skin’s innate exfoliating abilities.Vibrant makeup—including eye shadow palettes and eyeliners in varying colors—is another one of Estee Lauder’s specialties. From stay-in-place foundations to long-lasting lipsticks, the variety of cosmetics will give you endless options for style. Punctuate your coloring with a subtle touch of blush on both cheeks that will make you truly shine!When you want to enhance your eye color and shape, outline and shade with a dramatic eyeliner and darker hued eye shadows. Make your eyebrows pop with a brow pencil that features a brow color on once side and a blending brush on the other. Don’t forget to top off your beauty regimen with a splash of intoxicating perfume scents featuring notes like jasmine, honeysuckle and vanilla. It’s the finishing touch that lends grace and elegance instantly.For the complete range of Estee Lauder products, stop in at Macy’s today to find just what you’re looking for!











