Clinique Skin Care Est�e Lauder Est�e Lauder Women's Kate Spade Kate Spade New York Men's Cologne Ralph Lauren Ralph Lauren Men's Urban Decay Women's Clearance



Skin-CareTaking care of your skin is one of the most important parts of any beauty regimen. Starting your morning with the right facial cleanser and moisturizer can make all the difference. For those who want to pamper their skin, opt for overnight creams or weekly face masks designed to exfoliate and remove any dead skin cells. No matter what skin care regimen you decide on, you’ll find a variety of serums, creams, face washes and hydrating moisturizers.No facial cleanser is complete without the addition of a refreshing toner that clears away the excess oil naturally produced by your face. Follow with a lotion that will leave your face primed for makeup and eye shadow application.A consistent nighttime routine for your skin is also an essential part of keeping it healthy in the long run. A strong makeup remover is the first step in ensuring your face is free of dirt and oil before you go to bed. After removing your makeup, try a rejuvenating night cream that will firm and sculpt your face while working to reduce the appearance of wrinkles. Having trouble with dark circles? Try a dark circle corrector that will lighten and diminish dark circles over time. Get a more luminous skin tone with the skin-fortifying properties of a corrector that works to make your under eye areas less transparent. Don’t just focus on your face when it comes to skin care. There are also a wide variety of strengthening creams and concentrates for your neck and body that will help reduce the formation of wrinkles and stretch marks. Glycerin-based formulas are ideal as well when it comes to smoothing and illuminating your skin’s natural glow.Hydrate your eyes with a relaxing eye cream that will brighten and de-puff. Instead of a warm washcloth, try using a sonic cleanser that minimizes pores and enables skin to become much more open to absorbing serums and moisturizers.Regardless of what your skin care needs are, Macy’s has everything you could want to improve and sustain your skin’s beauty!











