Summer is speeding by, and our interns are more than halfway done with their ten week internships! Recently, our interns got to pick the brains of some of our millennial employees, asking about their work experiences, career advice, and what they love about being part of the #ELCfamily. To learn more about opportunities at our Company, visit www.elcompanies.com/talent.





For Chizuru, confidence came from her role in the beauty industry. Hear her story. #ELCfamily





#JoinOurFamily During an interview, tell us about the stimulating projects that you have worked on in current and previous roles. Our recruiters and hiring managers love to hear about your passions and achievements. #ELCfamily https://lnkd.in/d-QViVV








For Chizuru, confidence came from her role in the beauty industry. Hear her story. #ELCfamily



Happy Bastille Day to our friends, family and customers celebrating in France today! #ELCfamily #bastilleday



"There’s definitely a misconception about women working in the Middle East. Within the culture of The Estée Lauder Companies, we like to make sure that we have strong women.” Hear more from Rana about her role at our Company. #ELCfamily







It’s Friday! What is your favorite #maccosmetics shade for the weekend? #regram @maccosmetics #ELCfamily ⠀



The new #PepStart Double Bubble Purifying Mask reenergizes your skin in just two minutes… making it our go-to before just about everything #regram @Clinique #elcfamily #clinique⠀



Embracing days without our hair tools thanks to #bumbleandbumble 💁🏼💁🏾 #regram @bumbleandbumble @meaghanwozniakphoto #ELCfamily ⠀



















