Leading in Prestige Beauty

The Estée Lauder Companies’ strong and sustainable growth has helped drive the momentum in global prestige beauty — a dynamic, vibrant industry benefiting from favorable demographic trends.



150+
            Countries and Territories
            

25+
            Prestige Brands
            

$11.26 bn
            Total Net Sales
            


SOURCE: The Estée Lauder Companies, June 2016







Our success comes from our balanced and diversified business, powered by multiple engines of growth, coupled with agile resource allocation and excellent execution. We are the only major company focused solely on prestige beauty, with an unparalleled portfolio of more than 25 differentiated, aspirational brands suited to consumers in every region. Our strong financial position and cash flow from operations support our growth and acquisition strategy, which creates greater shareholder value. Read more




