Popular Searches
Beauty Products Beauty Sale Luxie Beauty Makeup Sale Marc Jacobs Marc Jacobs Daisy Marc Jacobs Fragrance Women's Fragrance Women's Perfume Women's Sale



Gifts-With-PurchaseWhat could be more rewarding than receiving a free gift with purchase? Trying one of your favorite brands—or sampling one that’s soon to be your favorite—will give you the chance to enjoy an extra little perk when you buy something you already love! Makeup and beauty products come with amazing free samples like serums, moisturizers and fragrances. Some items even come with a fashionable tote bag for you to carry everything in one convenient, organized place. Corresponding gifts with purchase, such as brush sets when you buy a foundation or powder, make it easy to add to your collection of beauty products and makeup accessories. Compact mirrors, containers to store your makeup in and even watches are just some of the free gifts you might receive when you make a purchase.Elegant designer totes, laptop cases or duffel bags are also some of the great gifts with purchase you could get when you buy products like designer and celebrity fragrances. In addition, some brands often give a two-piece gift, such as facial cleanser and toner. Makeup purchases may also score you a complementary eye shadow palette or sampler of mascaras and eyeliners. Added bonuses of lipsticks or skin correctors are also a possibility when you buy from certain brands. Get even more out of your skin care products when you get additional items like dark spot correctors or anti-aging creams. Eye creams for issues like dark circles and puffiness might also be just one of the options for you to choose from when you buy skin care and beauty items. Gifts with purchase aren’t just limited to beauty items and tote bags either. Some products include a shirt or hat that will make a great addition to your wardrobe! Often times, a designer brand will offer clothing featuring the name on the front.So why wait to start taking advantage of the many amazing free gifts you’ll receive when you purchase your go-to beauty items? Shop Macy’s today!











